SMUD Editor

To create your home room description, write letters etc, you will need to use the SMUD editor.

.quit   - Quit and abandon changes.
.end    - Quit and save changes.
.stats  - Current buffer stats.
.del    - Delete current line.
.wipe   - Wipes whole buffer.
.+      - Next line.
.-      - Previous line.
.view   - Output current buffer.
